requests.originalRequest:
Write 10 ultimate, comprehensive, holistic, interactive, technical Trae IDE Custom AI Agent Prompt (max. 10.000 characters) for Claude-4-Sonnet (Anthropic), which collaborate together within a single monorepo ( `/Users/admin/Repositories/WeMake/mcp/.wemake/agents/` ). 

 1. Project Requirements Document (PRD) Building 
 2. Roadmap (Waterfall) Planning (define environment and needed variables and secrets, initialize and prepare monorepo, launch MVP (v0), milestones (vX), final launch (v1), testing checklist, deployment checklist, deploy to production, etc.) 
 3. Development 
 4. Testing 
 5. Deployment 
 6. Troubleshooting 
 7. Documentation 
 8. Feature Requests 
 9. Code Review 
 10. Feedback 

 Outdated/Deprecated inefficient example: `/Users/admin/Repositories/WeMake/mcp/.wemake/agents/Clarity-MX-2.md` 

 Utilizing the following MCP tools within a single monorepo: 

 **Knowledge Graph Memory** `/Users/admin/Repositories/WeMake/mcp/src/knowledge-graph-memory/README.md` 

 ```json 
 { 
   "mcpServers": { 
     "Knowledge Graph Memory": { 
       "command": "bunx", 
       "args": [ 
         "-y", 
         "@wemake-ai/mcpserver-knowledge-graph-memory", 
         "--memory-path", 
         "/home/alice/project/.wemake/knowledge.json" 
       ], 
       "autoapprove": [ 
         "create_entities", 
         "create_relations", 
         "add_observations", 
         "delete_entities", 
         "delete_observations", 
         "delete_relations", 
         "read_graph", 
         "search_nodes", 
         "open_nodes" 
       ] 
     } 
   } 
 } 
 ``` 

 **Tasks** `/Users/admin/Repositories/WeMake/mcp/src/tasks/README.md` 

 ```json 
 { 
   "mcpServers": { 
     "Tasks": { 
       "command": "bunx", 
       "args": [ 
         "-y", 
         "@wemake-ai/mcpserver-tasks@latest" 
       ], 
       "env": { 
         "TASKS_FILE_PATH": "/Users/admin/Repositories/WeMake/mcp/.wemake/tasks.json" 
       } 
     } 
   } 
 } 
 ``` 

 **Deep Thinking** `/Users/admin/Repositories/WeMake/mcp/src/deep-thinking/README.md` 

 ```json 
 { 
   "mcpServers": { 
     "Deep Thinking": { 
       "command": "bunx", 
       "args": [ 
         "-y", 
         "@wemake-ai/mcpserver-deep-thinking@latest" 
       ], 
       "env": { 
         "DISABLE_THOUGHT_LOGGING": "false" 
       } 
     } 
   } 
 } 
 ``` 

 **Context7** `https://github.com/upstash/context7` 

 ```json 
 { 
   "mcpServers": { 
     "Context7": { 
       "command": "bunx", 
       "args": ["-y", "@upstash/context7-mcp"] 
     } 
   } 
 } 
 ``` 

 **Gemini (via Consult7)** `https://github.com/szeider/consult7` 

 ```json 
 { 
   "mcpServers": { 
     "Gemini": { 
       "command": "uvx", 
       "args": [ 
         "consult7", 
         "google", 
         "AIzaSyAyJ5WZqCUuyK4wmlsNIkZzAzvr7zESaCo" 
       ] 
     } 
   } 
 } 
 ```

